 class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">diagonal_eq_sum_single</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span>\n\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">min_imports</span>\n</code></pre></div><br>\n</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/31637\">#31637</a></p>",
